<p class="notice--primary"><strong>Watch out!</strong>
The communication via USB requires to install the serial driver <a href="https://www.silabs.com/products/development-tools/software/usb-to-uart-bridge-vcp-drivers">CP210x VCP from Silicon Labs</a>.</p>
